{"tid":1323973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察你地明唔明白宜家保護緊你地嘅係示威者心中嘅人道主義信仰","createTime":"2019-07-16T12:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T12:51:48.000Z","uid":55493,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"74ac274b5c99e87e873c403a0e6a55116262af04","tid":1323973,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"警察一步又一步踐踏人權，連取締連登都敢諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將市民賦予警察嘅公權力轉播成警察自己賦予自己嘅特權，凌駕於市民嘅人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若想有持續嘅特權警察只能討好市民，令市民唔主動收返你嘅公權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你宜家當正公權係特權老撚奉，<span style=\"color: red;\">賦予你公權力係方便你保護我地嘅人權，宜家你用特權欺壓市民，噉市民咪主動收返你嘅特權囉。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正如社會契約論，警察違約，噉自然基於呢份合約嘅內容就對市民冇約束力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇諗清楚抗爭者嘅底線係建基於心中對人權同人道主義嘅信仰，宜家警察竟然戇鳩到撕爛保護自己嘅防線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺人權畀警察撕爛晒之前，希望警察諗真啲，你地得幾萬人，喺唔講人道嘅市民面前，你地多多都唔夠死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用下腦，戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f6178322532e96b698a1cd51bf7986565eb7d6","tid":1323973,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"個個真係變哂暴徒佢地一早死哂啦"},{"pid":"2b7ff0bf04924f5fdb461d93f38ad0f0c0a169bf","tid":1323973,"uid":55493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"政權用警察保護自己，唔開獨立調查委員會係用警察做肉盾幫自己擋。<br />\n<br />\n警察畀人打，高官唔會救你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地咪睇下畀人圍個警察係邊個救返，係人道主義者呀，班高官呢？<br />\n<br />\n警察想安安樂樂長長久久保護自己唯有保障人權喺香港嘅地位，裝備保你一時保唔到你一世，宜家警察係都要自斷後路，醒少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民真係有好多好多好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你拉晒打晒班市民之前，警察收咗皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要搏畀市民收皮嘅唔係自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地以為警察真係好多人呀？戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef954508db47376578fd6160059f625c19718a1","tid":1323973,"uid":20916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"佢地第二段開始已經睇唔明"},{"pid":"5b53dc17852b22325a1e51ebe80960a517c4374d","tid":1323973,"uid":230861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"毅進仔撚聽得明咩公權人權咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f50c08a84a8c24e3e004790cd732c90f9e9fa24","tid":1323973,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"有腦仲會做黑犬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43abec58ba88fdd5b608bf8cabe66fbfb8cd74da","tid":1323973,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"推 警犬玩串個party"},{"pid":"2e99cfd47b4a2ce09a895df4ff86472bd80effbc","tid":1323973,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"有好多人留左案底，洗濕左個頭，唔洗諗後路，下次唔會再留手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11170aea4285e719ff8574a0b7b9f1f75c94c7b6","tid":1323973,"uid":69276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f586e37cf09e6fd6d556f6e677421ea8776f15bd","tid":1323973,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">畀警察睇最易理解版本</span><br />\n<br />\n警察內心：打低晒班暴徒，我地就好安全<br />\n<br />\n事實：警察越拉得多打得多，警察越危險，而且冇可能拉晒，由6月9開始，人越拉越多，但係警察處境越嚟越兇險，即係拉人唔能夠令警察變得安全<br />\n<br />\n建議：警察收手，越早離職越安全<br />\n<br />\n建議背後機理：<br />\n1. 唔當更咪冇危險，邊有示威者襲擊市民<br />\n2. 維護所有人包括示威者嘅人權，自然會保護埋自己嘅人權，唔明人權係咩唔緊要，明白人權係保命符就得<br />\n2.1 要保住自己嘅保命符有個條件就係善待示威者<br />\n2.2 人權亦係示威者嘅保命符，警察行動破壞緊人地嘅保命符，示威者自然要搏命<br />\n3. 警隊指揮冇將保警察命列入考慮，所以唯有離職"},{"pid":"9cc7de7cd2e09aacb336a1028cd34180fb3ff7c9","tid":1323973,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得我份人都算唔話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心救警察，高官都冇我噉著緊"},{"pid":"3afb95e946bb41070cc5a009ff7d7a95227c3525","tid":1323973,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc7de7cd2e09aacb336a1028cd34180fb3ff7c9","tid":1323973,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得我份人都算唔話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心救警察，高官都冇我噉著緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:51:48.000Z","msg":"高官根本就唔著緊<br />\n用完即棄"}]}